divs: Sighting DetailsBack of my business and saw what appeared to be 2 suns and a smaller object also round and like the sun in color moving with the 2 suns as they rotate. If you enlarge the smaller object you can see it is either a very large UFO or an asteroid or planet !? Also a lazer beam shot at my feet while taking these pics.
